column1: Following devices are not impacted by secure erase:
- HPE Smart Array MR controllers and connected storage
- SATA / SAS / NVM Express drives that do not support native sanitize methods
- GPGPU's / Other FPGA's / accelerators / offload engines that have keys or storage
